    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-strung S54B32 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline. This example utilizes a crisp 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis integrity has been proactively maintained with rear subframe reinforcement plates, and the VANOS unit has been serviced to ensure precise variable valve timing. The suspension geometry, consisting of McPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear, provides the communicative feedback and neutral handling balance synonymous with the M-division. While the exterior and cabin show minor patina consistent with a well-maintained driver\u2019s car, the powertrain remains robust with linear power delivery across the entire rev range.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
