    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of reliability and pride of ownership. Mechanically, it is in excellent working order; the engine pulls strong, the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, and there are no known leaks or warning lights on the dash. I have kept a meticulous log of all oil changes and scheduled maintenance. The exterior remains highly presentable with a deep, glossy finish, though a close inspection will reveal the typical minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches that come with regular use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free. The upholstery is well-preserved with only slight softening of the driver\u2019s side bolster, and all interior electronics\u2014including the premium sound system and dual-zone climate control\u2014operate exactly as they should. It sits on a set of tires with plenty of tread remaining, making this a truly turn-key car for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
