      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been such a gem to own. It's in really solid shape, runs like a dream, and has been well-cared for through the years. It\u2019s the perfect reliable ride for someone who wants quality without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019m looking for a smooth, quick sale, so I\u2019ve priced it to move! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love for this car to go to a great new home!",
