    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a well-sorted 2013 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the iconic S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving power unit delivers 414 hp with a linear power band peaking at 8,300 RPM. Mated to a 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission, the drivetrain remains crisp with precise shift logic. The chassis benefits from Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal lateral grip and torque vectoring. Recent proactive maintenance includes rod bearing replacement with treated shells and a fresh throttle actuator calibration. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited road use, the subframe and bushings remain tight. Mechanically robust and ready for the apex.",
